Notes

  • Analysis based on withdrawals that have both estimated finalization times and actual finalization times.
  • Positive errors mean that the actual finalization occurred later than estimated.
  • Negative errors mean that the actual finalization occurred earlier than estimated.
  • Data collected from DynamoDB table "lido_withdrawal_requests".
  • Withdrawals are processed in bulk once a day at roughly the same time.
  • Analysis timestamp: 2025-03-14 07:27:34 UTC
